{"tid":1994500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你哋可以當達哥係手足， 咁可唔可以當而家喺出面做緊嘢嘅我哋做手足？","createTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:58.000Z","uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3efcde6fc62d9a1e373614ad50f84ae3591ad7","tid":1994500,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"18區dse選民登記行動， 我哋呢幾日都係出面不斷咁派表， 不斷開post都冇人推， 就算你哋唔出嚟幫手都好， 可唔可以幫我哋推一推post， 至少畀想幫手嘅人趁而家加入我地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA&amp;d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&amp;h=daa23394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ft.me%252Fjoinchat%252FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA%26d%3DWEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%252BS4RyAur%252Bbp9MVyOkMM5%252FMxDY%253D%26h%3Ddaa23394&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=7844602d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA&amp;d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&amp;h=daa23394</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋仲有一日可以行動， 多一票就係多<br />\n<br />\n以下ig整合咗英文通識各區嘅考試場地， 大家可以去返自己區度派選民登記表。 sorry整得太樣衰,將會5月前盡快整合數學考試場地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_Po1negHE1/?igshid=1nogj89eexlpp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_Po1negHE1%2F%3Figshid%3D1nogj89eexlpp&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=32507770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_Po1negHE1%2F%3Figshid%3D1nogj89eexlpp&h=32b06f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B_Po1negHE1/?igshid=1nogj89eexlpp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2/5（星期六） 8:30 - 10:45 數學 必修部分 （一）<br />\n2/5 11:30 - 12:45 數學 必修部分 （二）<br />\n<br />\n詳細考試日期<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FExam_Timetable%2F2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=492d8cab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Exam_Timetable/2020_DSE_Timetable.pdf</a><br />\n試場查詢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=36fcb1e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n建議大家自行<br />\n印有QRcode單張 +派選民登記表格<br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=d2119826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民<br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=b1f2ddd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a4fcef56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=bec0207c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位等考生考完之後 先派選民登記表， 費事打亂佢哋嘅節奏"}]}